project_descr: The goal of electoral assistance is to help build and institutionalise national capacities to administer electoral processes credibly and sustainably, eventually without international support.

outputs.output_title: Supp to Electoral Cycle in S/L
outputs.output_descr: Improved National Electoral Commission (NEC) capacity to administer technically sound, inclusive and sustainable electoral processes that are capable of garnering public trust and confidence.
